-- Fixed text of quest 6824 (Hands of the Enemy): a pronoun was missing
UPDATE quest_template SET Details="$N, your service is of great value to us, so we are reluctant to send you on this last mission for we do not want to lose such a useful agent.$B$BBut its success would further our war efforts tremendously and... it was deemed worth risking you.$B$BWe want these captains in the Molten Core destroyed: Lucifron, Sulfuron, Gehennas and Shazzrah.  Kill them and bring me their hands!$B$BThis task will take every resource you possess, $N, but if you can do it then the Firelords will be dealt a terrible blow." WHERE entry=6824;
